file: test/smart.test.ts
purpose: Integration tests for `renderSmart`, `renderPlain`, and `buildSmartDict` against the real `dict.steno` dictionary. Verifies cursor-placement logic, trailing-closer suppression, parity with plain rendering, and collision-free dict construction.
invariants:
  - Tests load and parse the actual `dict.steno` file at module scope; all `get()` calls assert non-null.
